# Step 1 / 8 — SCAN

Identify the EA codebase shape and the friction points worth fixing.

## Inputs
- Repository checkout
- Issue / motivation note (≤ 200 words)

## Activities
- [ ] List `.mq5` / `.mqh` files touched in the last 30 days
- [ ] Run `mql5-lint` on the entry-point EA → capture WARN / ERROR counts
- [ ] Read any prior `step-8-refine.md` to inherit context

## Outputs
- `step-1-scan.md` — pain-point catalogue, listed paths, lint baseline

## Exit criteria
- Pain points ranked by impact
- Decision recorded: continue to RRI, or stop (no useful change to ship)

> Sentinel: when this step is complete, `touch .rri-state/scan.done`.
